    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, ensuring optimal camshaft timing and torque delivery across the rev range. To address chassis longevity, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced with plates. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension kinematics remain sharp thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the communicative feedback this platform is famous for. Finished with an interior that shows honest use but remains intact, this car is primed for technical driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
