      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, having been frequently waxed and garage-kept. While there are minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful city driving, the body remains straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery shows only light bolstering wear on the driver's seat, and the carpets have been protected by weather-resistant mats since day one. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It features a complete service history with recent oil and filter changes, a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires, and brakes that offer firm, confident stopping power. It drives smoothly with no unusual noises or vibrations, reflecting a life of proactive maintenance rather than reactive repairs. This is an honest, reliable car for a discerning buyer who values a documented history and a well-preserved driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
